==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Emplaster
<hw>Em*plas"ter</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Cf. OF.
<ets>emplastrer</ets>, F. <ets>empl⟦acir⟧trer</ets>. See
